System Requirements\
-------------------\
Same requirements as the OJS 2.1.x core.\
\
Installation\
------------\
To install the plugin:\
 - enable the plugin by going to:  Home > User > Journal Management > Plugin Management  and selecting "ENABLE" under "CMS RSS Plugin"\
\
Configuration\
------------\
In order to configure this plugin, the CMS plugin must be installed and enabled.  Furthermore, there must be at least 1 page in the CMS.  RSS feed aggregations are added to _already existing_ CMS pages.  This plugin does NOT create new pages, it simply appends to an existing page.  In order to create a page that only has the RSS feed, you must create a blank page in the CMS Plugin (by placing only an Heading).\
\
